{"tid":2277351,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"青山醫院被勒索9000萬","createTime":"2020-11-08T11:52:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T15:20:14.000Z","uid":250828,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"7526e8327490495ed5286115e0f1f1f3efa95af8","tid":2277351,"uid":250828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T11:52:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/hk/1917814\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1917814&d=TOASGvm2FfjCvYiV2fDq71tn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=92b8e5b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/hk/1917814</a><br />\n<br />\n屯門青山醫院一名女職員，昨午收到勒索9000萬元的電郵，報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n現場為青松觀路。警方昨午3時47分接獲47歲女職員報案，指收到一封電郵，被勒索約9000萬元。<br />\n<br />\n警員經初步調查，案件暫列勒索，交由屯門警區刑事調查隊第九隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n用電郵勒索青山醫院9000萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以留定床位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abec6339345b62cdea995abc8ede2acd1ad426ce","tid":2277351,"uid":70487,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T11:54:02.000Z","msg":"會員青山走犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d727d9bd17a496d494a9414d05db6d56d5c3059d","tid":2277351,"uid":54930,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T11:54:05.000Z","msg":"想打尖入青山<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8c4d10513ce3d7f0ae28c22aadd2ea5cfe723bf","tid":2277351,"uid":252680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T11:54:10.000Z","msg":"高招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c609cd57b0c0a172690fe089ab9c418f1b4